{"type": "article", "id": 52471, "title": "把单车变成墙面装饰物，只需要一个挂架｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2018-04-23T23:03:58Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 49613, "name": "Xivestory"}, {"id": 49614, "name": "Moustache"}, {"id": 49615, "name": "Classicon"}, {"id": 28432, "name": "Neri&Hu"}, {"id": 49616, "name": "Artifox"}, {"id": 15542, "name": "Remko Verhaagen"}, {"id": 49617, "name": "Anna Auras"}, {"id": 22997, "name": "Ionna Vautrin"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 16, "praise_count": 167, "image": "img/article/article_show/20180423222029Wjine9JpucORYb15.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000; min-height: 13.0px} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} span.s4 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Rack by Artifox</h3><p>如何在家中存放自行车？Artifox 给出的解决方案，是一款名为 Rack 的自行车架，允许用户把自行车挂在墙上，解决室内空间不够的问题。</p><p>Rack 的结构很简单，白枫木或是黑胡桃木搭配粉末涂层钢架，结实耐用，安装简单，然后直接把自行车挂上去即可，不仅解决收纳问题，也是一个足够特别的墙面装饰品。售价 199 美元，<a href=\"https://theartifox.com/products/rack-black\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180423222116uA9tSK6aqp2HbgQW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.593519\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180423222118WS3CpD9wcAiTMKJ6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180423222118ZHwMN08CfEenY61J.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180423222118sVWudw3DULcZHltJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180423222118fxmMPKywd0osSuUV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180423222119fHQTWBLt41cFkmpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>LANTERN LIGHT by Neri&amp;Hu for Classicon</h3><p>意大利建筑设计师 Vico Magistretti 在 1977 年设计了名为 Lyndon 的系列灯具，采用线条简单的灯柱和球形的光源，形成有趣的对比，整只灯有如一朵发光的云彩。在 Vico Magistretti 逝世十周年之际，德国家具品牌 Classicon 邀请如恩特别设计了“灯笼”系列灯具，向 Lyndon 灯致敬。</p><p>“灯笼”灯的设计灵感源自光的精髓，就像光的最早形式，火炬一样。在暗色玻璃罩保护下的光源置于柱状支撑结构的顶端，强调了光源本身，散发出柔和的光芒。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180423222230umxe7cWIR6pEbMso.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.523677\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180423222232d3yFghSerYa7OIi5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.504202\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180423222232vq2HkZlEGp0DbTe9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667491\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180423222234FU8ZvMRe50qVaBTh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180423222235PwhCoZtzre2T0891.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.661290\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180423222234yU1NVCOIqKxQBAgv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.664188\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://www.classicon.com/en/product/lantern-light-floor-lamp.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">Classicon</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>TGV Table Lamp by Ionna Vautrin for Moustache</h3><p>巴黎家具品牌 Moustache，与目前国际设计圈耀眼的设计师们有不少合作，像是 Big-Game、Jean-Baptiste Fastrez、  Constance Guisset、Bertjan Pot、Inga Sempé 等人 ，开发优雅摩登的当代家具家居用品。他们充满艺术性实验感的作品被收藏于全球各大艺术设计博物馆中。</p><p>在米兰设计周期间，Moustache 联合 SNCF 法国国家铁路在米兰发布了一款 TGV 台灯。这款由法国设计师 Ionna Vautrin 设计的桌面台灯，同时也是法国铁路第一次尝试生产销售进入家庭领域的灯具。从公共领域的灯饰转换到家庭来使用，希望给居家环境带去新鲜和惊喜感。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180423224726vBxfypIc9Am6o1Sk.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666016\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180423224726Q46IGLPEOBd5e0Z9.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180423224726d0M4bgshEvlkfBYG.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180423224726Pv1Uo7hSHG3lXyjN.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.207031\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2018042322472591P3obnEYqseZOj2.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666016\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：Moustache</figcaption></figure></div><h3>Circles Collection by Atelier Auras</h3><p>Anna Auras 被人称作是兼有艺术家和工匠精神的设计师，她对平面设计和摄影等艺术学科的广泛兴趣，也在她的珠宝作品中留下了鲜明的痕迹。</p><p>这个 Circles 系列的灵感源自俄国前卫艺术家和艺术理论家 Kazimir Malevich 于 1915 年发起的艺术运动 Suprematism，每一款都是 Anna 手工制作而成。Circles 系列巧妙地搭配几何图案，由项链，耳钉和小号及大号耳环组成。清晰的圆形和精致的轮廓赋予了每件作品华丽的样式。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180423224754zDbVq9hG6kJ2ot3e.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180423224755qKLspmkAalQhvVB1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180423224754aCYV5efLop2t1jD9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180423224756iCStFRHGAgLQjrsb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180423224756yBsAnKtDYhlPZdkg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://annaauras.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Atelier Auras</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Pila by Remko Verhaagen</h3><p>Pila 是一种传统的危地马拉水槽，这是一种一物多用的盥洗漕，用来清洗衣服和餐具。</p><p>荷兰设计师 Remko Verhaagen 最近重新诠释了 Pila，为安提瓜岛中心的时尚精品酒店量身而做。设计师希望通过这个作品，将住店游客与安提瓜岛当地的历史联系起来，而 Pila 是个不错的选择，融合了当地殖民地风格和极简主义风格，提供黑色大理石、白色大理石以及大理石和水泥的混合版本，另配有柚木托盘和废物篮可供选择。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180423224827ZCDMU6uxcvVbjzFn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180423224828IOzawtC4gcbKx2Nd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180423224828cmNyhXdGTwJbxakE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180423224828oZtGlSUcyKmjPau9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180423224830eOx8LyDJI3QSa40k.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.497500\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.blooey.nl/good-hotel-pila\" rel=\"nofollow\">blooey.nl</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>AniBite by Xivestory</h3><p>Xivestory 设计了一款咬合挂架 AniBite，有猎豹、狗熊、野狼三种造型，每只都是伶牙俐齿，张着血盆大口，感觉像是时刻准备着撕咬猎物。</p><p>AniBite 具有一键式开启和关闭功能，它的用途很广泛，适用于存放牙刷、钥匙、钢笔、眼镜等。AniBite 由 PETG 和 PCTG 等安全无毒塑料制成，背面附有 PU 凝胶，可以附着在任何平面或是有轻微凸起纹理的表面上，且不会留下任何痕迹。当粘附力变弱时，只要用水清洗背部即可。众筹价 15 美元，<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1026442059/anibite-one-touch-multi-holder-for-all-small-belon?ref=afainv\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180423225330UjLbJSp7Xr5limsx.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.560554\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180423225330RTM7SCo6EAZU9K2L.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.560886\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180423224920YmPSMKDqCHiFx9Ty.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.052381\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180423224920XvdpA2lIckDyexga.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180423224920nIgTGXNSzO2D6uLR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180423224920a0CwRmjnk8YNsOKL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180423224920wC701tHjKiUyPeOf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180423224920NhPBAHs9Xt2EIwnl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.761905\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}